Description: Open, pharma-specific blocks for blockr. Provides a no-code
    patient profile for clinical safety review on CDISC ADaM data: stacked,
    time-aligned visualizations (adverse events, labs, vitals, questionnaire
    scores) driven from a 'dm' of ADaM tables.
